寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=ff5ea228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"306fd9b3f1c2911bf3c57619191fda3014057eab","tid":1551691,"uid":296108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"香港人就如正義，只會遲到，不會缺席"},{"pid":"d233bab76ebc4cdf08087af93714a9142c3646ae","tid":1551691,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f102f069609d3e3be96cde7e346e9f398f64fc9","tid":1551691,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"邊個位入到"},{"pid":"d972099327360599ea52c771262698149e6753c9","tid":1551691,"uid":314825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"出緊嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5b4dd86defc49cc538736893ba94ce8c6396fa","tid":1551691,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不流血不受傷不被捕不分化不篤灰不割蓆追究警察濫權 五大訴求缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7ee7a5d3f560934d04e9a5b0707e97a454c1ae4b",